  "description": "You can call on even more powerful divine intervention. When you use your Divine Intervention feature, you can choose Wish when you select a spell. If you do so, you can't use Divine Intervention again until you finish [[/r 2d4]] Long Rests.\n\nFoundry Note\n\nThis feature will consume a use of your Divine Intervention but it can not automatically recharge the usage after the rolled number of Long Rests.",
